&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/SanskritYatra-Sloka.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">नवग्रहसूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Navgruhsuktam
&lt;div id="navgruhsuktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#navgruhsuktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ शुक्लाम्बरधरं विष्णुं शशिवर्णं चतुर्भुजम्। &lt;br>
प्रसन्नवदनम् ध्यायेत्सर्व विघ्नोपशान्तये॥ &lt;br>
ॐ भूः ॐ भुवः॑ ॐ सुवः॑ ॐ महः॑ ॐ जनः ॐ तपः॑ ॐ स॒त्यम् &lt;br>
ॐ तत्स॑वि॒तुर्वरे᳚ऽण्यं॒ भर्गो॑दे॒वस्य॑ धीमहि धियो॒ यो नः॑ प्रचो॒दया᳚ऽत् ॥ &lt;br>
ॐ आपो॒ ज्योती॒रसो॒ऽमृतं॒ ब्रह्म॒ भूर्भुव॒स्सुव॒रोम् ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>ममोपात्त-समस्त-दुरितक्षयद्वारा श्रीपरमेश्वर प्रीत्यर्थं आदित्यादि नवग्रह देवता &lt;br>
प्रसाद सिध्यर्तं आदित्यादि नवग्रह नमस्कारान् करिष्ये॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>भूसूक्तम् - भूसूक्तम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/bhoosuktam/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/bhoosuktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Durga.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">भूसूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Bhoosuktam
&lt;div id="bhoosuktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#bhoosuktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ भूमि॑र्भू॒म्ना द्यौर्व॑रि॒णाऽन्तरि॑क्षं महि॒त्वा । &lt;br>
उ॒पस्थे॑ ते देव्यदिते॒ऽग्निम॑न्ना॒द-म॒न्नाद्या॒याद॑धे ॥ &lt;br>
आऽयङ्गौः पृश्नि॑रक्रमी॒ दस॑नन्मा॒तरं॒ पुनः॑ । &lt;br>
पि॒तरं॑ च प्र॒यन्त्सुवः॑ ॥ त्रि॒ग्ं॒शद्धाम॒ विरा॑जति॒ वाक्प॑त॒ङ्गाय॑ शिश्रिये । &lt;br>
प्रत्य॑स्य वह॒ द्युभिः॑ ॥ अ॒स्य प्रा॒णाद॑पान॒त्य॑न्तश्च॑रति रोच॒ना । व्य॑ख्यन् महि॒षः सुवः॑ ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>यत्त्वा᳚ क्रु॒द्धः प॑रो॒वप॑म॒न्युना॒ यदव॑र्त्या । सु॒कल्प॑मग्ने॒ तत्तव॒ पुन॒स्त्वोद्दी॑पयामसि ॥ &lt;br>
यत्ते॑ म॒न्युप॑रोप्तस्य पृथि॒वीमनु॑दध्व॒से । &lt;br>
आ॒दि॒त्या विश्वे॒ तद्दे॒वा वस॑वश्च स॒माभ॑रन् ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Narayan Suktam- नारायणसूक्तम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/narayan-suktam/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/narayan-suktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Vishnu.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">नारायणसूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Narayan Suktam
&lt;div id="narayan-suktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#narayan-suktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/036-narayanSuktam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>सहस्रशीर्षं देवं विश्वाक्षं विश्वशम्भुवम् । &lt;br>
विश्वं नारायणं देवं अक्षरं परमं पदम् ।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>विश्वतः परमान्नित्यं विश्वं नारायणग्ं हरिम् । &lt;br>
विश्वं एवेदं पुरुषस्तद्विश्वं उपजीवति ।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>पतिं विश्वस्यात्मेश्वरग्ं शाश्वतग्ं शिवमच्युतम् । &lt;br>
नारायणं महाज्ञेयं विश्वात्मानं परायणम् ।&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Purush Suktam - पुरुषसूक्त</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/purush-suktam/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/purush-suktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Durga.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">पुरुषसूक्त
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Purush Suktam
&lt;div id="purush-suktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#purush-suktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/039-purushSuktam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>अथ पुरुषसूक्तम् ॥ &lt;br>
ॐ तच्छं॒ योरावृ॑णीमहे । गा॒तुं य॒ज्ञाय॑ । &lt;br>
गा॒तुं य॒ज्ञप॑तये । दैवी᳚ स्व॒स्तिर॑स्तु नः । &lt;br>
स्व॒स्तिर्मानु॑षेभ्यः । ऊ॒र्ध्वं जि॑गातु भेष॒जम् । &lt;br>
शन्नो॑ अस्तु द्वि॒पदे᳚ । शं चतु॑ष्पदे । &lt;br>
ॐ शान्तिः॒ शान्तिः॒ शान्तिः॑ ।&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Vaak Suktam - वाक्सूक्तम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/vaak-suktam/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/vaak-suktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Vipasana.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">वाक्सूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Vaak Suktam
&lt;div id="vaak-suktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#vaak-suktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ दे॒वीं वाच॑मजनयन्त दे॒वाः । तां वि॒श्वरू॑पाः प॒शवो॑ वदन्ति । &lt;br>
सा नो॑ म॒न्द्रेष॒मूर्जं॒ दुहा॑ना । धे॒नुर्वाग॒स्मानुप॒सुष्टु॒तैतु॑ । &lt;br>
यद्वाग्वद॑न्त्यविचेत॒नानि॑ । राष्ट्री॑दे॒वानां᳚ निष॒साद॑म॒न्द्रा । &lt;br>
चत॑स्र॒ ऊर्जं॑ दुदुहे॒ पयाग्ं॑सी । क्व॑स्विदस्याः पर॒मं ज॑गाम । &lt;br>
अ॒न॒न्तामन्ता॒दधि॒ निर्मि॑तां म॒हीम् । यस्यां᳚ दे॒वा अ॑दधु॒र्भोज॑नानि । &lt;br>
एका᳚ख्षरां द्वि॒पदा॒ग्ं॒ षट्॑पदां च । वाचं॑ दे॒वा उप॑जीवन्ति॒ विश्वे᳚ । &lt;br>
वाचं॑ दे॒वा उप॑जीवन्ति॒ विश्वे᳚ । वाचं॑ गन्ध॒र्वाः प॒शवो॑ मनु॒ष्याः᳚ । &lt;br>
वा॒ची मा विश्वा॒ भुव॑ना॒न्यर्पि॑ता । सा नो॒ हवं॑ जुषता॒मिन्द्र॑पत्नी । &lt;br>
वाग॒ख्षरं॑ प्रथम॒जा ऋ॒तस्य॑ । वेदा॑नां मा॒ताऽमृत॑स्य॒ नाभिः॑ । &lt;br>
सा नो॑ जुषा॒णोप॑ य॒ज्ञमागा᳚त् । अव॑न्ती दे॒वी सु॒हवा॑ मे अस्तु । &lt;br>
या मृष॑यो मन्त्र॒कृतो॑ मनी॒षिणः॑ । अ॒न्वैच्छ॑न्दे॒वास्तप॑सा॒ श्रमे॑ण । &lt;br>
तां दे॒वीं वाचग्ं॑ ह॒विषा॑ यजामहे । सा नो॑ दधातु सुकृ॒तस्य॑ लो॒के । &lt;br>
च॒त्वारि॒वाक्परि॑मिता प॒दानि॑ । तानि॑ विदुर्ब्राह्म॒णा ये म॑नी॒षिणः॑ । &lt;br>
गुहा॒ त्रीणि॒ निहि॑ता॒ नेङ्ग॑यन्ति । तु॒रीयं॑ वा॒चो म॑नु॒ष्या॑ वदन्ति ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>GanpatyaTharvShirshopnishad - गणपत्यथर्वशीर्षोपनिषत्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/ganpatyatharvshirshopnishad/</link><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/ganpatyatharvshirshopnishad/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/GaneshJi.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">गणपत्यथर्वशीर्षोपनिषत्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">GanpatyaTharvShirshopnishad
&lt;div id="ganpatyatharvshirshopnishad" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#ganpatyatharvshirshopnishad" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ भ॒द्रं कर्णे॑भिः श‍ृणु॒याम॑ देवाः । भ॒द्रं प॑श्येमा॒क्षभि॒र्यज॑त्राः । &lt;br>
स्थि॒रैरङ्गै᳚स्तुष्टु॒वाग्ं स॑स्त॒नूभिः॑ । व्यशे॑म दे॒वहि॑तं॒ यदायुः॑ । &lt;br>
स्व॒स्ति न॒ इन्द्रो॑ वृ॒द्धश्र॑वाः । स्व॒स्ति नः॑ पू॒षा वि॒श्ववे॑दाः । &lt;br>
स्व॒स्ति न॒स्तार्क्ष्यो॒ अरि॑ष्टनेमिः । स्व॒स्ति नो॒ बृह॒स्पति॑र्दधातु ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>शान्तिः॒ शान्तिः॒ शान्तिः॑ ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>नम॑स्ते ग॒णप॑तये । त्वमे॒व प्र॒त्यक्षं॒ तत्त्व॑मसि । &lt;br>
त्वमे॒व के॒वलं॒ कर्ता॑ऽसि । त्वमे॒व के॒वलं॒ धर्ता॑ऽसि । &lt;br>
त्वमे॒व के॒वलं॒ हर्ता॑ऽसि । त्वमेव सर्वं खल्विदं॑ ब्रह्मा॒सि । &lt;br>
त्वं साक्षादात्मा॑ऽसि नि॒त्यम् ॥ १ ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Pavmaan Suktam - पवमानसूक्तम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/pavmaan-suktam/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/pavmaan-suktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">पवमानसूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Pavmaan Suktam
&lt;div id="pavmaan-suktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#pavmaan-suktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ ॥ हिर॑ण्यवर्णाः॒ शुच॑यः पाव॒का यासु॑ जा॒तः क॒श्यपो॒ यास्विन्द्रः॑ । &lt;br>
अ॒ग्निं या गर्भं॑ दधि॒रे विरू॑पा॒स्ता न॒ आप॒श्शग्ग् स्यो॒ना भ॑वन्तु ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>यासा॒ग्ं॒ राजा॒ वरु॑णो॒ याति॒ मध्ये॑ सत्यानृ॒ते अ॑व॒पश्यं॒ जना॑नाम् । &lt;br>
म॒धु॒श्चुत॒श्शुच॑यो॒ याः पा॑व॒कास्ता न॒ आप॒श्शग्ग् स्यो॒ना भ॑वन्तु ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>यासां᳚ दे॒वा दि॒वि कृ॒ण्वन्ति॑ भ॒क्षं या अ॒न्तरि॑क्षे बहु॒धा भव॑न्ति । &lt;br>
याः पृ॑थि॒वीं पय॑सो॒न्दन्ति शु॒क्रास्ता न॒ आप॒श्शग्ग् स्यो॒ना भ॑वन्तु ॥ &lt;br>
शि॒वेन॑ मा॒ चक्षु॑षा पश्यतापश्शि॒वया॑ त॒नुवोप॑ स्पृशत॒ त्वचं॑ मे । &lt;br>
सर्वाग्ं॑ अ॒ग्नीग्ं र॑प्सु॒षदो॑ हुवे वो॒ मयि॒ वर्चो॒ बल॒मोजो॒ निध॑त्त ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Bhagya Shuktam- भाग्य सूक्तम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/bhoo-shuktam/</link><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/bhoo-shuktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">भाग्य सूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Bhagya Shuktam
&lt;div id="bhagya-shuktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#bhagya-shuktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ प्रा॒तर॒ग्निं प्रा॒तरिन्द्रग्ं॑ हवामहे प्रा॒तर्मि॒त्रा वरु॑णा प्रा॒तर॒श्विना᳚ । &lt;br>
प्रा॒तर्भगं॑ पू॒षणं॒ ब्रह्म॑ण॒स्पतिं॑ प्रा॒तः सोम॑मु॒त रु॒द्रग्ं हु॑वेम ॥१ ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>प्रा॒त॒र्जितं॒ भ॑गमु॒ग्रग्ं हु॑वेम व॒यं पु॒त्र-मदि॑ते॒र्यो वि॑ध॒र्ता । &lt;br>
आ॒द्ध्रश्चि॒द्यं मन्य॑मानस्तु॒रश्चि॒द्राजा॑ चि॒द्यं भगं॑ भ॒क्षीत्याह॑ ॥ २ ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>भग॒ प्रणे॑त॒-र्भग॒ सत्य॑राधो॒ भगे॒मां धिय॒मुद॑व॒दद॑न्नः । &lt;br>
भग॒प्रणो॑ जनय॒ गोभि॒-रश्वै॒र्भग॒प्रनृभि॑-र्नृ॒वन्त॑स्स्याम ॥३ ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Aayshman Suktam - आयुष्य सूक्तम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/aayshman-suktam/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/aayshman-suktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/SanskritYatra-Sloka.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">आयुष्य सूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AF-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Aayshman Suktam
&lt;div id="aayshman-suktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#aayshman-suktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>यो ब्रह्मा ब्रह्मण उ॑ज्जहा॒र प्रा॒णैः शि॒रः कृत्तिवासाः᳚ पिना॒की । &lt;br>
ईशानो देवः स न आयु॑र्दधा॒तु॒ तस्मै जुहोमि हविषा॑ घृते॒न ॥ १ ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>विभ्राजमानः सरिर॑स्य म॒ध्या॒-द्रो॒च॒मा॒नो घर्मरुचि॑र्य आ॒गात् । &lt;br>
स मृत्युपाशानपनु॑द्य घो॒रा॒नि॒हा॒यु॒षे॒णो घृतम॑त्तु दे॒वः ॥ २ ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>ब्रह्मज्योति-र्ब्रह्म-पत्नी॑षु ग॒र्भं॒ य॒मा॒द॒धात् पुरुरूपं॑ जय॒न्तम् । &lt;br>
सुवर्णरम्भग्रह-म॑र्कम॒र्च्यं॒ त॒मा॒यु॒षे वर्धयामो॑ घृते॒न ॥ ३ ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Medha Suktam - मेधासूक्तं</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/medha-suktam/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/medha-suktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">मेधासूक्तं
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Medha Suktam
&lt;div id="medha-suktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#medha-suktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>तैत्तिरीयारण्यकम् – ४ प्रपाठकः १० – अनुवाकः ४१-४४&lt;/p>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/043-MedhaSuktam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>ॐ यश्छन्द॑सामृष॒भो वि॒श्वरू॑पः। छन्दो॒भ्योऽध्य॒मृता᳚थ्संब॒भूव॑। &lt;br>
स मेन्द्रो॑ मे॒धया᳚ स्पृणोतु। अ॒मृत॑स्य देव॒धार॑णो भूयासम्। &lt;br>
शरी॑रं मे॒ विच॑र्षणम्। जि॒ह्वा मे॒ मधु॑मत्तमा। &lt;br>
कर्णा᳚भ्यां॒ भूरि॒विश्रु॑वम्। ब्रह्म॑णः को॒शो॑ऽसि मे॒धया पि॑हितः। &lt;br>
श्रु॒तं मे॑ गोपाय। ॐ शान्तिः॒ शान्तिः॒ शान्तिः॑ ॥&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>